allHistorySummary:
Day 22: Congestion, Interjections, and Exclamations
- Congestion: Crowding or blocking (e.g., traffic congestion)
- Interjections: Short words expressing strong emotion (e.g., Wow!, Ouch!)
- Exclamations: Phrases expressing strong feelings (e.g., What a beautiful day!, I'm so happy!)
User understood concepts readily.
